標題：頭盔（helmet）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： כּוֹבַע</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kova‘)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:5\">1SA 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:14\">2CH 26:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:17\">ISA 59:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:4\">JER 46:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:10\">EZK 27:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:5\">EZK 38:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מָעוֹז, רֹאשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ma‘oz ro’sh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps60:9\">PSA 60:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps108:9\">PSA 108:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： קוֹבַע</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： qova‘)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:38\">1SA 17:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:24\">EZK 23:24</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： περικεφαλαία</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： perikefalaia)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:17\">EPH 6:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:8\">1TH 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:35\">1MA 6:35</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κόρυς</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： korus)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis5:18\">WIS 5:18</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0971_helmet.jpg\" alt=\"頭盔\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">頭盔 (© Public Domain - Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>頭盔是保護頭部的護甲。有些頭盔設計有垂邊，延伸至耳朵甚至頸部。以色列人和他們的鄰邦所使用的頭盔通常用皮革製成。金屬頭盔非常罕有，一般是從東面和北面的一些國家進口。參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.3.1 鞘 (sheath, scabbard)&lt;REALIA:2.3.1&gt;</a> 中的插圖。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0973_helmet.jpg\" alt=\"士兵戴的頭盔\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">士兵戴的頭盔 (© Jona Lendering - Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>如果目標語言沒有表示「頭盔」的詞語，翻譯者可以採用描述性的同義詞，例如「保護頭部的裝備」或「戰鬥時戴的頭套」。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:17\">ISA 59:17</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:17\">EPH 6:17</a> 中，「救恩的頭盔」這個比喻可以譯為「救恩好像頭部的護具」。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
